thub.com/edward-goreys-great-simple-theory-about-art-is-essential-reading-for-writers/"><img src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gorey-copy-150x150.jpg" alt="" /></a></div><strong class="title"><a href="https://lithub.com/edward-goreys-great-simple-theory-about-art-is-essential-reading-for-writers/">Edward Gorey's "Great Simple Theory About Art" is essential reading for writers.</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center">February 19, 2025 by <a href="https://lithub.com/author/emily-temple/">Emily Temple</a><div class="post_comment_count"><a href="https://lithub.com/edward-goreys-great-simple-theory-about-art-is-essential-reading-for-writers/" title="Edward Gorey's "Great Simple Theory About Art" is essential reading for writers."><i class="fa fa-comments-o"></i>0</a></div></span></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><div class="article_num">4.</div><a href="https://lithub.com/what-robert-frosts-philosophy-of-the-human-spirit-says-about-his-artistic-ethos/"><img src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/frost-150x150.jpg" alt="" /></a></div><strong class="title"><a href="https://lithub.com/what-robert-frosts-philosophy-of-the-human-spirit-says-about-his-artistic-ethos/">What Robert Frost’s Philosophy of the Human Spirit Says About His Artistic Ethos</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center">February 18, 2025 by <a href="https://lithub.com/author/adamplunkett/">Adam Plunkett</a><div class="post_comment_count"><a href="https://lithub.com/what-robert-frosts-philosophy-of-the-human-spirit-says-about-his-artistic-ethos/" title="What Robert Frost’s Philosophy of the Human Spirit Says About His Artistic Ethos"><i class="fa fa-comments-o"></i>0</a></div></span></li></ul></li>
